workflow.code:
Start:
    Book a flight
    Inquire the user for the Flight ID
    call checkAvailability to confirm flight status
    check flight availability based on the returned is_air
    if Flight is available:
        Tell the user that the flight is available
        Ask the user for ID number and name
        call reserveFlight
        check if the reservation is successful based on the returned is_successful
        if Reservation succeeded:
            Inform the user that the reservation succeeded
            Notify the user of booking details based on other returned values of reserveFlight
            Ask if the user wants to book again
            if User books again:
                goto Book a flight
            else if User does not rebook:
                The user is welcome to contact again for future needs
        else if Reservation failed:
            Notify the user that the reservation failed
            Ask if the user wants to book again
            if User books again:
                goto Book a flight
            else if User does not rebook:
                The user is welcome to contact again for future needs
    else if Flight is unavailable:
        Inform the user that the flight is unavailable
        Confirm if the user wants to book another flight
        if User books another flight:
            goto Book a flight

