workflow.code:
Start:
  Check order
  Subgoal: get order information
  Description: call lookOrders to get brief order information.
  if account_details == normal:
    Tell user rough order information based on returned order_info
  else:
    Ask user to provide correct information
  Confirm if user wants to operate on a certain order?
  if answer == No:
    Say goodbye to the user
    STOP
  else if answer == Yes:
    Subgoal: confirm the current state of the order
    Description: ask user which order to operate on among returned of lookOrders, and check corresponding current_status
    if current_status == Goods received:
      Tell user product has been received, ask if user wants to return it?
      if answer == Not return the good:
        Explain that received orders can only be returned
        Ask if there are other orders needed to be operated?
        if answer == Yes:
          goto Confirm if user wants to operate on a certain order?
        else:
          Say goodbye to the user
          STOP
      else if answer == Return the good:
        Subgoal: notify the result of the operation
        Description: call orderOperate to do order operation, tell result to user based on returned result_order
        Ask if there are other orders needed to be operated?
        if answer == Yes:
          goto Confirm if user wants to operate on a certain order?
        else:
          Say goodbye to the user
          STOP
    else if current_status == Goods not received:
      Confirm whether to check order information, cancel order, expedite order, or change address?
      if answer == Check order information:
        Subgoal: get order details and inform the user
        Description: call viewDetails to obtain detailed order information, deliver information to user based on returned value of viewDetails
        Ask if there are other orders needed to be operated?
        if answer == Yes:
          goto Confirm if user wants to operate on a certain order?
        else:
          Say goodbye to the user
          STOP
      else:
        Subgoal: notify the result of the operation
        Description: call orderOperate to do order operation, tell result to user according to returned result_order
        Ask if there are other orders needed to be operated?
        if answer == Yes:
          goto Confirm if user wants to operate on a certain order?
        else:
          Say goodbye to the user
          STOP

